0Crime%20Against%20Women%20Cell.%20Each%20squad%20will%20consist%20of%20an%20inspector%2C%20a%20sub-inspector%2C%20and%20four%20female%20and%20five%20male%20police%20officers%20(Assistant%20Sub-Inspectors%2C%20head%20constables%2C%20and%20constables).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20personnel%20from%20special%20staff%20or%20Anti-Auto%20Theft%20Squad%20(AATS)%20will%20accompany%20the%20squad%20for%20technical%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squads'%20primary%20focus%20will%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bhotspots%20and%20vulnerable%20areas%26quot%3B%20that%20pose%20risks%20to%20women's%20safety.%20The%20District%20Deputy%20Commissioners%20of%20Police%20(DCPs)%20will%20identify%20and%20compile%20a%20list%20of%20hotspots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squad%20will%20be%20required%20to%20conduct%20drives%20in%20at%20least%20two%20vulnerable%20points%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20squads%20will%20operate%20with%20a%20multi-faceted%20approach%20involving%20prevention%2C%20intervention%2C%20and%20victim%20assistance%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20squads%20will%20be%20dressed%20in%20civil%20clothes%20to%20identify%20and%20deter%20offenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20squads%20shall%20conduct%20surprise%20checks%20in%20public%20transport%20and%20interact%20with%20DTC%20drivers%2C%20conductors%2C%20and%20passengers%20and%20motivate%20them%20to%20report%20such%20incidents%2C%26quot%3B%20executive%20directions%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20DCPs%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%20ensuring%20that%20the%20squads%20are%20sensitive%2C%20empathetic%2C%20and%20self-motivated.%20%26quot%3BVictims%20should%20be%20protected%20from%20unnecessary%20public%20scrutiny%20or%20embarrassment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20follows%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police's%20%26quot%3Banti-Romeo%26quot%3B%20drive%20launched%20in%202017%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20men%20harassing%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A174218034