%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Doval%20and%20Ms%20Gabbard%20mainly%20discussed%20ways%20to%20strengthen%20intelligence%20sharing%20and%20working%20closely%20in%20the%20security%20domain%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20India-US%20global%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gabbard%20arrived%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20early%20Sunday%20on%20a%20two-and-a-half-day%20trip%20in%20the%20first%20high-level%20visit%20to%20India%20by%20a%20top%20official%20of%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%26quot%3Bgood%20discussion%26quot%3B%2C%20top%20sources%20told%20PTI%20on%20the%20Doval-Gabbard%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%2C%20Canadian%20spy%20chief%20Daniel%20Rogers%2C%20and%20UK%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Jonathan%20Powell%20were%20among%20top%20global%20intelligence%20czars%20who%20attended%20the%20India-hosted%20security%20conclave%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliberations%20were%20held%20behind%20closed%20doors%20and%20there%20was%20no%20official%20word%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20top%20intelligence%20and%20security%20officials%20focused%20on%20sharing%20of%20intelligence%20and%20cooperation%20to%20tackle%20terrorism%20and%20threats%20posed%20by%20emerging%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20focused%20on%20security%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20cooperation%20to%20counter%20terror%20funding%20and%20money%20laundering%20and%20issues%20relating%20to%20extradition%20and%20immigration%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20also%20raised%20its%20concerns%20about%20anti-India%20elements%20operating%20from%20foreign%20soil%2C%20including%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntelligence%20chiefs%20of%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20several%20other%20friendly%20countries%20of%20India%20were%20learnt%20to%20have%20attended%20the%20conclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gabbard%20is%20visiting%20India%20as%20part%20of%20a%20multi-nation%20tour%20of%20Japan%2C%20Thailand%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20intelligence%20chief%20will%20also%20address%20the%20Raisina%20Dialogue%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Gabbard%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Washington%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20deliberations%2C%20the%20intelligence%20chiefs%20were%20understood%20to%20have%20deliberated%20on%20various%20global%20challenges%20including%20implications%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%20to%20India%20by%20Canadian%20Security%20Intelligence%20Service%20(CSIS)%20chief%20Rogers%20has%20taken%20place%20amid%20frosty%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20over%20the%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20following%20the%20then%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20in%20September%202023%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20rejected%20Trudeau's%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B.%20The%20relations%20nosedived%20further%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20last%20year%20after%20Ottawa%20linked%20several%20Indian%20diplomats%20including%20High%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Verma%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%2C%20Canada%20expelled%20Mr%20Verma%20and%20five%20other%20diplomats.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20New%20Delhi%20also%20expelled%20Canadian%20Charge%20d'Affaires%20Stewart%20Wheeler%20and%20five%20other%20diplomats.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20case%20may%20figure%20during%20Doval's%20