%20of%20AI%20models%20is%20named%20%26quot%3BErnie.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERegis%20Martin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20tech%20giant%20Baidu%20released%20open-source%20AI%20models%20Ernie%20X1%20and%20Ernie%204.5.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20says%20the%20models%20rival%20those%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20DeepSeek%20in%20performance%20per%20cost.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20models%20also%20further%20the%20AI%20industry's%20turn%20toward%20open-source.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBaidu%2C%20China's%20answer%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20released%20two%20new%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESaturday%2C%20Baidu%20released%20Ernie%20X1%2C%20a%20reasoning%20model%20it%20says%20%26quot%3Bdelivers%20performance%20on%20par%20with%20DeepSeek%20R1%20at%20only%20half%20the%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20launched%20a%20multimodal%20foundation%20model%20called%20Ernie%204.5%20that%20the%20company%20says%20%26quot%3Boutperforms%20GPT-4.5%20in%20multiple%20benchmarks%20while%20priced%20at%20just%201%25%20of%20GPT-4.5.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaidu%20said%20it's%20also%20making%20its%20chatbot%2C%20Ernie%20Bot%2C%20free%20to%20the%20public%20on%20April%201%2C%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giant%20said%20it%20will%20%26quot%3Bprogressively%20integrate%26quot%3B%20Ernie%204.5%20and%20X1%20into%20its%20product%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20Baidu%20Search%2C%20China's%20dominant%20search%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaidu's%20new%20releases%20come%20as%20Silicon%20Valley%20reckons%20with%20the%20cost%20of%20AI%20models%2C%20largely%20spurred%20by%20the%20latest%20drops%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-deepseek-r1-china-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Chinese%20startup%20launched%20by%20hedge%20fund%20High%20Flyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20DeepSeek%20released%20a%20large%20language%20model%20called%20V3%2C%20and%20in%20January%2C%20it%20unveiled%20a%20reasoning%20model%20called%20R1.%20The%20models%20are%20considered%20as%20good%20or%20better%20than%20equivalent%20models%20from%20OpenAI%20but%20priced%20%26quot%3Banywhere%20from%2020-40x%20cheaper%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ai-lab-deepseek-massively-undercuts-openai-on-pricing-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%20from%20Bernstein%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22004f76de-54a0-4b30-9851-191cafd77efd%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20vs%20DeepSeek%20vs%20Baidu%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETokens%20are%20the%20smallest%20unit%20of%20data%20an%20AI%20model%20processes.%20Companies%20price%20models%20according%20to%20how%20many%20input%20tokens%20a%20model%20processes%20and%20output%20tokens%20it%20generates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Ernie%204.5%2C%20Baidu%20said%20that%20input%20and%20output%20token%20prices%20start%20as%20low%20as%200.004%20Chinese%20yuan%20per%20thousand%20input%20tokens%20and%200.016%20per%20thousand%20output%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20converted%20those%20figures%20into%20US%20dollars%20to%20understand%20how%20chat%20models%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20DeepSeek%2C%20and%20Baidu%20compare%20against%20one%20another.%20While%20Baidu's%20cost%20claims%20against%20OpenAI's%20latest%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-releases-gpt-4-5-emotionally-intelligent-model-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemotionally%20intelligent%26quot%3B%20GPT-4.5%3C%2Fa%3E%20check%20out%2C%20DeepSeek's%20V3%20barely%20wins%20out%20in%20cost%20against%20Ernie%204.5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Baidu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d75226b8b41a9673facd47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20converted%20to%20USD%2C%20Ernie%204.5%20costs%20about%20%240.55%20per%20million%20input%20tokens%20and%20%242.2%20per%20million%20output%20tokens.%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4.5%20costs%20%2475%20for%20the%20same%20number%20of%20input%20tokens%20and%20%24150%20for%20output%20tokens.%20In%20comparison%20to%20GPT-4.5%2C%20R1%20and%20Ernie%204.5%20demonstrate%20a%2098-99%25%20drop%20in%20cost.%20%3Cp%3EBI%20via%20Flourish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20reasoning%20models%2C%20conversions%20to%20USD%20show%20that%20Ernie%20X1%20is%20the%20cheapest%20of%20all%20with%20prices%20just%20under%202%25%20of%20OpenAI's%20o1.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22reasoning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d752bdb8b41a9673facd4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EX1%20costs%20%240.28%20per%20million%20input%20tokens%20and%20%241.1%20per%20million%20output%20tokens.%20OpenAI's%20models%20are%20priced%20at%20%2415%20and%20%2460%20for%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20tokens.%20%3Cp%3EBI%20via%20Flourish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECost-savings%20aside%2C%20those%20who've%20already%20tried%20Ernie%20seem%20impressed.%20%26quot%3BBeen%20playing%20around%20with%20it%20for%20hours%2C%20impressive%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Alvin%20Foo%2C%20a%20venture%20partner%20at%20Zero2Launch%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaidu's%20latest%20models%20demonstrate%20not%20only%20the%20growing%20competition%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20but%20also%20the%20latter's%20growing%20embrace%20of%20open-source%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20we%20learned%20from%20DeepSeek%20is%20that%20open-sourcing%20the%20best%20models%20can%20greatly%20help%20adoption%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi