sation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20fasting%20right%20now.%20It%20has%20been%20almost%20two%20days%2C%2045%20hours.%20So%2C%20just%20water%2C%20no%20food%2C%20in%20honour%20of%20this%20conversation%2C%20just%20to%20get%20in%20the%20right%20mindset%2C%20get%20into%20the%20spiritual%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bpleasantly%20surprised%26quot%3B%20to%20know%20that%20Mr%20Fridman%20was%20fasting%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20more%20because%20it%20feels%20like%20you're%20fasting%20as%20a%20tribute%20of%20respect%20for%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20express%20my%20deepest%20gratitude%20to%20you%20for%20doing%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20emphasised%20the%20benefits%20of%20fasting%20in%20sharpening%20the%20senses%2C%20enhancing%20mental%20clarity%2C%20and%20instilling%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFasting%20is%20a%20way%20to%20cultivate%20discipline...%20It%20is%20a%20powerful%20tool%20to%20bring%20both%20the%20inner%20and%20outer%20self%20into%20balance.%20It%20shapes%20life%20in%20profound%20ways.%20When%20you%20fast%2C%20every%20single%20one%20of%20your%20senses%2C%20especially%20smell%2C%20touch%2C%20and%20taste%2C%20becomes%20highly%20sensitive.%20Another%20thing%20I've%20experienced%20is%20that%20fasting%20can%20greatly%20accelerate%20the%20thinking%20process%20and%20can%2C%20uh%2C%20give%20a%20fresh%20perspective.%20You%20start%20thinking%20outside%20the%20box%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20PM%20Met%20Obama%20While%20Fasting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-lex-fridman-russia-ukraine-pm-modis-not-time-for-war-message-for-putin-brother-advice-for-zelensky-7936343%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20shared%20an%20episode%20when%20he%20met%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20while%20fasting.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20I%20had%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20at%20the%20White%20House%20with%20President%20Obama%2C%20and%20he%20had%20also%20arranged%20a%20formal%20dinner.%20Then%2C%20as%20discussions%20between%20the%20two%20governments%20progressed%2C%20someone%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%2C%20join%20us%20for%20dinner.%26quot%3B%20To%20which%20another%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doesn't%20eat.%26quot%3B%20This%20left%20them%20a%20bit%20concerned.%20How%20do%20you%20host%20the%20leader%20of%20such%20a%20major%20nation%20at%20the%20White%20House%20without%20serving%20food%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20he%20was%20then%20served%20a%20glass%20of%20hot%20water.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20sat%20down%2C%20they%20brought%20me%20a%20glass%20of%20hot%20water.%20I%20turned%20to%20President%20Obama%20and%20jokingly%20said%2C%20'Look%2C%20my%20dinner%20has%20arrived!'%20as%20I%20placed%20the%20glass%20in%20front%20of%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20met%20Mr%20Obama%20the%20next%20time%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20remembered%20I%20was%20fasting%20the%20last%20time%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BHe%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20'Last%20time%2C%20you%20were%20fasting'.%20This%20time%2C%20we're%20having%20lunch.%20Since%20you're%20not%20fasting%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20eat%20twice%20as%20much%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-podcast-with-lex-fridman-criticism-is-soul-of-democracy-7936255%5C%22%3EPM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20stressed%20that%20fasting%20%26quot%3Bis%20actually%20a%20scientific%20process%26quot%3B%20while%20sharing%20how%20he%20prepares%20before%20fasting%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%20%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20fast%20for%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20I%20prepare%20my%20body%20in%20advance.%20For%205%20to%207%20days%20before%20the%20fast%2C%20I%20follow%20various%20Ayurvedic%20practices%20and%20yoga%20practices%2C%20along%20with%20other%20traditional%20cleansing%20methods%20to%20internally%20reset%20my%20system%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20actually%20beginning%20the%20fast%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20drink%20a%20lot%20of%20water%2C%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20So%2C%20you%20could%20say%20that%20this%20detoxification%20process%20helps%20prepare%20my%20body%20in%20the%20best%20possible%20way.%20And%20once%20I%20begin%20fasting%2C%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20an%20act%20of%20devotion.%20For%20me%2C%20fasting%20is%20a%20form%20of%20self-discipline%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20PM%20Fasted%20For%201st%20Time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20recalled%20the%20first%20time%20he%20experienced%20fasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20my%20school%20days%2C%20there%20was%20a%20movement%20inspired%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20vision%2C%20his%20vision%20of%20cow%20protection.%20The%20government%20had%20not%20enacted%20any%20laws%20at%20the%20time.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20people%20across%20the%20country%20observed%20a%20one-day%20fast%20by%20gathering%20in%20public%20places%20in%20silent%20protest.%20We%20were%20just%20kids%2C%20probably%20had%20just%20finished%20primary%20school.%20Something%20inside%20me%20said%2C%20'I%20should%20be%20part%20of%20this%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20such%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20felt%20neither%20hunger%20nor%20any%20desire%20for%20food.%20Instead%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20new%20awareness%2C%20a%20surge%20of%20energy%20within%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20became%20convinced%20that%20fasting%20is%20a%20science%2C%20far%20beyond%20just%20skipping%20meals.%20It%20is%20something%20far%20greater%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20fasting%20never%20slows%20him%20down%2C%20rather%20makes%20him%20more%20energetic.%20%26quot%3BI%20work%20just%20as%20much%20as%20usual%2C%20sometimes%20I%20even%20work%20more%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742144400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8ucfu9s8_pm-modi-lex-fridman_625x300_16_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-on-lex-fridman-podcast-why-lex-fridman-fasted-for-45-hours-before-podcast-with-pm-modi-7936706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20wide-ranging%20conversation%20with%20American%20scientist%20Lex%20Fridman%20in%20a%20podcast%20that%20was%20released%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-on-lex-fridman-podcast-why-lex-fridman-fasted-for-45-hours-before-podcast-with-pm-modi-7936706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShe%20Herself%20Used%20Tamil%20Letter%26quot%3B%3A%20MK%20Stalin%20On%20N%20Sitharaman's%20%26quot%3BRupee%26quot%3B%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefending%20his%20government's%20move%20to%20replace%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20with%20the%20Tamil%20letter%20'Ru'%20in%20the%20state%20Budget%20logo%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20even%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20had%20used%20the%20Tamil%20letter%20instead%20of%20the%20rupee%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20alleged%20those%20opposing%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Tamil%20language%20blew%20the%20issue%20out%20of%20proportion.%20He%20told%20reporters%20the%20decision%20was%20a%20reflection%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20commitment%20to%20its%20language%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20state%20has%20been%20on%20a%20warpath%20with%20the%20Centre%20over%20implementing%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterestingly%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20herself%20used%20the%20Tamil%20letter%20instead%20of%20Re%20%5Bfor%20rupee%5D%20in%20English%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Stalin%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20remove%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Budget%202025-26%20logo%2C%20presented%20on%20March%2014%2C%20drew%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20AIADMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20alleged%20the%20DMK%20has%20been%20engaging%20in%20regional%20politics%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20national%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20condemned%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government's%20decision%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20completely%20avoidable%20example%20of%20language%20and%20regional%20chauvinism.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20removing%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20signalled%20%26quot%3Ba%20dangerous%20mindset%20that%20weakens%20Indian%20unity%20and%20promotes%20secessionist%20sentiments%20under%20the%20pretence%20of%20regional%20pride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20reminded%20elected%20representatives%20of%20their%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20uphold%20national%20sovereignty%2C%20adding%20the%20DMK's%20move%20contradicted%20this%20commitment.%20She%20highlighted%20the%20irony%20behind%20the%20decision%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20was%20designed%20by%20D%20Udaya%20Kumar%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20DMK%20MLA%20N%20Dharmalingam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20erasing%20it%20now%2C%20the%20DMK%20is%20not%20only%20rejecting%20a%20national%20symbol%20but%20also%20utterly%20disregarding%20the%20creative%20contribution%20of%20a%20Tamil%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Amit%20Malviya%20slammed%20Mr%20Stalin%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20was%20designed%20in%20Devanagari%20script%20by%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20General%20Secretary%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%2C%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%2C%20called%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublicity%20stunt%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20administrative%20failures.%20He%20accused%20Mr%20Stalin%20of%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bempty%20advertisement%20campaigns%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20addressing%20real%20needs%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunching%20a%20strong%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Stalin%20and%20his%20party%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20asked%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20How%20foolish%20can%20you%20become%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20DMK%20Government's%20State%20Budget%20for%202025-26%20replaces%20the%20Rupee%20Symbol%20designed%20by%20a%20Tamilian%2C%20which%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20whole%20of%20Bharat%20and%20incorporated%20into%20our%20Currency.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThiru%20Udhay%20Kumar%2C%20who%20designed%20the%20symbol%2C%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20former%20DMK%20MLA.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHow%20stupid%20can%20you%20become%2C...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ft3ZyaVmxmq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ft3ZyaVmxmq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20K.Annamalai%20(%40annamalai_k)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fannamalai_k%2Fstatus%2F1900103792299041115%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2013%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20said%20the%20Budget%20logo%20aims%20to%20reflect%20the%20state's%20linguistic%20identity.%20The%20logo%20also%20carries%20the%20caption%20%26quot%3BEverything%20for%20All%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20the%20DMK%20said%20embodies%20its%20inclusive%20governance%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20Centre%20responded%20only%20to%20the%20rupee%20symbol%20issue%20while%20ignoring%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20demands%20for%20disaster%20relief%2C%20education%20funds%2C%20and%20employment%20schemes.%20The%20DMK%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20imposing%20Hindi%2C%20and%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20rupee%20symb