ent.%20The%20world%20had%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20terrorist%20activities%20and%20violence%20during%20those%20times.%20However%2C%20since%202002%2C%20not%20a%20single%20case%20of%20riots%20has%20occurred%20in%20Gujarat.%20He%20also%20highlighted%20that%20people%20tried%20to%20malign%20his%20image%20after%20the%20riots%20but%20ultimately%2C%20justice%20prevailed%20and%20the%20courts%20cleared%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20backdrop%20in%20which%20the%20events%20took%20place%2C%20he%20named%20the%20Kandahar%20hijack%2C%20the%209%2F11%20attack%20in%20the%20US%2C%20attacks%20on%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%20and%20parliament.%C2%A0These%20events%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Bcreated%20the%20background%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BIn%20such%20a%20tense%20environment%2C%20even%20the%20smallest%20spark%20can%20ignite%20unrest.%20The%20situation%20had%20already%20become%20extremely%20volatile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20was%20handed%20the%20responsibility%20of%20leading%20Gujarat%20as%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20amid%20the%20massive%20quake%20in%20Bhuj%20and%20the%20rehabilitation%20efforts%20that%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20crucial%20task%2C%20and%20from%20day%20one%20after%20my%20oath%2C%20I%20immersed%20myself%20in%20it.%20I%20was%20a%20person%20who%20had%20absolutely%20no%20prior%20experience%20with%20government.%20I%20had%20never%20been%20part%20of%20any%20administration%2C%20never%20even%20served%20in%20government%20before.%20I%20had%20never%20contested%20an%20election%2C%20never%20even%20been%20a%20State%20Representative.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20had%20to%20face%20elections.%20On%20February%2024%2C%202002%2C%20I%20became%20a%20State%20Representative%2C%20an%20elected%20representative%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20And%20it%20was%20only%20around%20February%2024th%2C%2025th%2C%20or%2026th%20that%20I%20stepped%20into%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time.%20On%20February%2027%2C%202002%2C%20we%20were%20seated%20in%20the%20assembly%20for%20the%20budget%20session%2C%20and%20that%20same%20day%2C%20it%20had%20been%20just%20three%20days%20since%20I'd%20become%20a%20State%20Representative%2C%20when%20suddenly%2C%20the%20horrific%20Godhra%20incident%20occurred%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btragedy%20of%20unimaginable%20magnitude%2C%20people%20were%20burned%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20imagine%2C%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20incidents%20like%20the%20Kandahar%20hijacking%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Parliament%2C%20or%20even%209%2F11%2C%20and%20then%20to%20have%20so%20many%20people%20killed%20and%20burned%20alive...%20You%20can%20imagine%20how%20tense%20and%20volatile%20the%20situation%20was.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20was%20tragic%20for%20everyone%2C%20everyone%20prefers%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumming%20up%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20was%20a%20long%20history%20long%20before%20I%20was%20in%20the%20picture.%20But%20that%20one%20tragic%20incident%20in%202002%20became%20a%20sparking%20point%2C%20leading%20some%20people%20towards%20violence.%20Yet%2C%20the%20judiciary%20thoroughly%20investigated%20the%20matter.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20our%20political%20opponents%20were%20in%20power%2C%20and%20naturally%2C%20they%20wanted%20all%20allegations%20against%20us%20to%20stick%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20their%20relentless%20efforts%2C%20the%20judiciary%20analyzed%20the%20situation%20meticulously%2C%20twice%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20found%20us%20completely%20innocent.%20Those%20who%20were%20truly%20responsible%20have%20faced%20justice%20from%20the%20courts%2C%26quot%3Bhe%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20that%20that%20the%202002%20riot%20as%20the%20biggest%20ever%20is%20actually%20misinformation%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20review%20the%20data%20from%20before%202002%2C%20you'll%20see%20that%20Gujarat%20faced%20frequent%20riots%2C%20curfews%20were%20constantly%20being%20imposed%20somewhere.%C2%A0Communal%20violence%20could%20erupt%20over%20trivial%20issues%2C%20like%20kite-flying%20contests%20or%20even%20minor%20bicycle%20collisions.%20Before%202002%2C%20Gujarat%20witnessed%20over%20250%20significant%20riots.%20The%20riots%20in%201969%20lasted%20nearly%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20years%20since%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20a%20single%20instance%20of%20communal%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20said.%20With%20the%20policy%20of%20%26quot%3BSabka%20Saath%2C%20sabka%20vikaas%2C%20sabka%20Vishwas%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement%20has%20been%20changed%20into%20politics%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742140140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fa2j4m6do_pm-modi-lex-fridman-ians_625x300_16_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-on-lex-fridman-podcast-pm-modi-on-2002-godhra-riots-a-tragedy-of-unimaginable-magnitude-7936780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202002%20Sabarmati%20Express%20attack%20in%20Gujarat's%20Godhra%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btragedy%20of%20unimaginable%20magnitude%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20riots%20that%20followed%20this%20%26quot%3Bwas%20tragic%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-on-lex-fridman-podcast-pm-modi-on-2002-godhra-riots-a-tragedy-of-unimaginable-magnitude-7936780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20sends%20Venezuelan%20gang%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20members%20to%20El%20Salvador%22%2C%22con