nt-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrand-new%20Peppa%20Pig%20amusement%20park%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Florida%20that%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20our%20kids%20to.%20Our%20kids%20loved%20the%20show%2C%20and%20the%20park%20seemed%20age-appropriate%20for%20our%20then%204-year-old%20and%202-year-old%20twins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20park%20was%20next%20to%20Legoland%20Florida%2C%20and%20tickets%20for%20both%20parks%20were%20pretty%20affordable%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-free-travel-agent-plan-disney-trip-big-group-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompared%20to%20Disney%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20we%20went%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20loved%20the%20Legoland%20park%20so%20much%20that%20we%20ended%20up%20taking%20them%20to%20the%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-kid-friendly-city-travel-guide-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20New%20York%20in%20later%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20three%20parks%20compare%2C%20and%20which%20I%20love%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20parks%20have%20some%20overlap%2C%20though%20they%20offer%20slightly%20different%20experiences.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20at%20Legoland%20California%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d32fb069253ccddf99320d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20loved%20the%20submarine%20ride%20at%20Legoland%20California.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20parks%20from%20the%20same%20franchise%2C%20all%20three%20Legolands%20feature%20very%20similar%20attractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20layouts%20are%20different%2C%20and%20the%20order%20in%20which%20you%20enter%20each%20world%20may%20vary%2C%20you%20pretty%20much%20can%