en%2C%20kind%20face%20and%20a%20calming%20presence.%20The%20most%20surprising%20reaction%20I%20had%20was%20a%20voice%20inside%20my%20head%20that%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20there%20you%20are!%26quot%3B%20as%20if%20I'd%20been%20waiting%20for%20an%20old%20friend%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20dismissed%20this%20because%20it%20sounded%20kooky%20and%20deluded.%20I%20was%2030%2C%20single%2C%20emotionally%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falways-do-a-proper-breakup-with-partner-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebruised%20from%20a%20break-up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20a%20very%20unsuitable%20person%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20of%20packing%20up%20my%20life%20to%20work%20in%20Sydney%2C%2010%2C000%20miles%20away.%20The%20instant%20sense%20of%20ease%20and%20familiarity%20I%20felt%20when%20I%20saw%20Will%20was%20just%20my%20mind%20playing%20tricks.%20I%20naturally%20presumed%20he%20was%20engaged%2Fmarried%2Fcohabiting%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20cross%20my%20mind%20to%20find%20out.%20When%20I%20caught%20his%20eye%2C%20and%20he%20smiled%2C%20I%20smiled%20back%20and%20turned%20away%20(blushing%20furiously).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20that's%20when%20fate%20intervened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a71e525-a085-4658-af29-6f02f901b607%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20him%20the%20time%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-discontinue-ipod-after-21-years-iconic-music-player-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EiPod%20ran%20out%20of%20battery%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20so%20I%20put%20it%20in%20my%20bag%20and%20took%20out%20my%20phone.%20The%20battery%20had%20also%20died%20%E2%80%94%20odd%2C%20it%20was%20half-full%20when%20I%20left%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20so%20I%20checked%20my%20watch%20to%20see%20what%20time%20it%20was.%