nts%20say%20they're%20nearing%20a%20breakthrough.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAdvocates%20say%20quantum%20computers%20could%20revolutionize%20many%20industries%20if%20they%20achieve%20their%20potential.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20alone%20if%20you've%20been%20hearing%20the%20buzz%20about%20quantum%20computing%20and%20wondering%20what%20it%20means%20or%20why%20it%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapidly%20evolving%20field%20remains%20deeply%20technical%2C%20expensive%20to%20advance%2C%20and%20not%20yet%20particularly%20useful%20for%20anyone%20other%20than%20researchers.%20While%20small-scale%20quantum%20computers%20exist%2C%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-race-big-tech-microsoft-google-amazon-ibm-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBM%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20racing%20to%20scale%20them%20up%20to%20commercial%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20investments%20are%20intended%20to%20usher%20in%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20ultra-powerful%20computers%20capable%20of%20performing%20advanced%20computations%20impossible%20for%20classical%20computers.%20While%20some%20researchers%20argue%20sufficient%20advancement%20in%20the%20field%20could%20someday%20usher%20in%20science-fiction-sounding%20outcomes%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphysicists-built-a-time-machine-simulator-2015-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20a%20broader%20consensus%20that%2C%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%20quantum%20computing%20will%20bring%20about%20major%20advancements%20in%20medicine%2C%20materials%20science%2C%20and%20other%20fields%20that%20would%20profoundly%20impact%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%5C%5C%3C%2Fstrong%3EMichael%20Biercuk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Australian%20quantum%20infrastructure%20software%20company%20Q-CTRL%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20some%20of%20the%20earliest%20applications%20for%20quantum%20computing%20are%20%26quot%3Bjust%20not%20very%20sexy%2C%20but%20they%20are%20economically%2C%20extremely%20high%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20with%20over%20a%20dozen%20people%20in%20the%20quantum%20computing%20field%2C%20including%20researchers%20from%20IBM%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20the%20executives%20behind%20startups%20including%20Q-CTRL%20and%20QuamCore%2C%20and%20scholars%20running%20some%20of%20the%20top%20quantum%20labs%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20they%20say%20are%20the%20most%20promising%20ways%20quantum%20computing%20could%20change%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247beb3fc-6d68-4e45-8561-dd86a7325d9e%5C%22%3EImproved%20logistics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20major%20opportunity%20for%20true%20quantum%20advantage%20is%20logistics%20optimization%20and%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20Bieruck%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20very%20challenging%20problems%2C%20and%20we%20know%20they%20are%20computationally%20bottlenecked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimizing%20supply%20chains%20and%20improving%20logistics%20operations%20can%20make%20major%20organizations%20like%20the%20military%20and%20global%20shipping%20industry%20more%20efficient%2C%20helping%20businesses%20ensure%20consistent%20quality%20and%20reliable%20supply.%20This%20could%20also%20drive%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20consumer%20goods%2C%20reduce%20waste%2C%20and%20prevent%20spoilage%20of%20perishable%20items%2C%20potentially%20addressing%20larger%20social%20problems%20like%20world%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abf558a7-8480-4927-bfbf-53703e8a6bb4%5C%22%3ENew%20building%20materials%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELighter%20and%20more%20durable%20materials%20used%20to%20create%20roads%20and%20bridges%2C%20houses%2C%20and%20other%20everyday%20items%20could%20make%20construction%20quicker%20and%20more%20affordable%20and%20reduce%20the%20need%20for%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20earliest%20applications%20that%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20tackle%20that%20are%20relevant%20and%20provide%20not%20just%20utility%2C%20but%20also%20an%20advantage%20with%20a%20quantum%20computer%20over%20any%20classical%20computer%20is%20in%20the%20area%20of%20material%20science%20and%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Oskar%20Painter%2C%20the%20director%20of%20quantum%20hardware%20at%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20late%20February%2C%20following%20the%20company's%20announcement%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-debuts-ocelot-chip-quantum-computing-race-google-microsoft-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOcelot%20chip%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20promising%20is%20the%20potential%20discovery%20of%20self-healing%20materials%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0imagine%20buildings%20created%20of%20metals%20that%20repair%20themselves%20or%20asphalt%20that%20fills%20in%20its%20own%20cracks%20%E2%80%94%20could%20also%20be%20possible%20through%20quantum%20computing%2C%20Microsoft%20teased%20in%20its%20February%20press%20release%20announcing%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMajorana%201%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ace2a68-222a-46ac-af46-500451060ad1%5C%22%3EMore%20efficient%20batteries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOptimizing%20battery%20materials%20at%20the%20molecular%20level%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20more%20efficient%20and%20powerful%20batteries%2C%20improving%20the%20range%20of%C2%A0electric%20vehicles%20and%20increasing%20electrical%20grid%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20could%20be%20opportunities%20where%20the%20energy%20density%20could%20go%20way%20up%20just%20because%20you%20have%20a%20better%20matrix%20other%20than%20carbon%20for%20storing%20lithium%20ions%2C%20like%20we%20do%20conventionally%20in%20current%20LiPo%20batteries%2C%26quot%3B%20Painter%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20things%20that%20I%20would%20say%20aren't%20so%20glamorous%20when%20you%20talk%20about%20them%2C%20but%20they%20can%20have%20some%20major%20real-world%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220183f71d-d564-4820-9419-2d4ea706a322%5C%22%3EDrug%20discovery%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Schoelkopf%2C%20chief%20scientist%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Quantum%20Circuits%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20quantum%20computing%20might%20help%20us%20speed%20up%20the%20discovery%20of%20new%20drugs%20by%20identifying%20new%20compounds%C2%A0with%20higher%20efficacy%20and%20fewer%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20full-scale%20quantum%20computer%2C%20drug%20discovery%20times%20will%20go%20from%2015%20years%20to%20five%20years%2C%20maybe%20to%20three%20years%20to%20two%20years%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20problem%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20solved%2C%26quot%3B%20Schoelkopf%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230224127-7fd6-48ba-9e8d-aaafdcea96ca%5C%22%3EBreaking%20encryption%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20more%20ominously%2C%20quantum%20computing%20also%20shows%20security%20researchers%20one%20way%20that%20we%20know%20will%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%26quot%3B%20lead%20to%20our%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencryption%20methods%20being%20broken%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Karl%20Holmqvist%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Lastwall%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20provider%20of%20quantum%20resilient%20technology%20used%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20that's%20internet-connected%20will%20likely%20have%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Holmqvist%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20trust%20that%20the%20links%20between%20systems%20are%20secure%20and%20the%20data%20that's%20gone%20between%20them%20is%20secure%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20get%20into%20those%20that%20they're%20encrypted.%20If%20you%20take%20away%20that%20default%20assumption%2C%20it%20allows%20so%20many%20new%20entry%20points%20into%20systems%20that%20it%20becomes%20quite%20concerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArthur%20Herman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Quantum%20Alliance%20Initiative%20at%20Hudson%20Institute%2C%20added%20that%20sufficient%20advancements%20in%20quantum%20computing%20could%20undermine%20the%20security%20of%20any%20encrypted%20data%2C%20from%20financial%20transactions%20stored%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-blockchain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblockchain%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20national%20security%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20talking%20about%20is%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hack%2C%20not%20just%20into%20individual%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20but%20our%20larger%20financial%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Herman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd5c87b-695b-456c-806b-cdd85012981b%5C%22%3E%E2%80%A6but%20we're%20not%20there%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we%20are%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20demonstrating%20quantum%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20IBM's%20VP%20of%20quantum%20adoption%20and%20business%20development%2C%20Scott%20Crowder%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20when%20a%20quantum%20computer%20outperforms%20classical%20machines.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20industry%20is%20still%20a%20few%20years%20from%20a%20fully%20fault-tolerant%20quantum%20computer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20he%20added%2C%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20need%20to%20be%20cautious%20about%20raising%20the%20public's%20expectations%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-say-major-quantum-computing-breakthroughs-are-years-away-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromoting%20breakthroughs%20in%20their%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20avoid%20creating%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver-hype%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20industry%2C%20Crowder%20said%2C%20could%20lead%20people%20to%20discount%20quantum%20technology%20before%20its%20promise%20can%20be%20realized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20when%20the%20industry%20eventually%20solves%20its%20problems%20with%20error%20correction%20and%20scalability%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20Crowder%20said%20he%20believes%20is%20imminent%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Blike%20science%20fiction%20come%20to%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-could-improve-medicine-climate-logistics-world-hunger-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742124002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678aebacae09223df2ba973c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-could-improve-medicine-climate-logistics-world-hunger-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20Tech%20companies%20are%20heavily%20invested%20in%20quantum%20computing%20development.%20While%20unstable%2C%20the%20technology%20could%20change%20medicine%20and%20other%20fields.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A153%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-could-improve-medicine-climate-logistics-world-hunger-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fixing%20the%20US%20Navy's%20shipbuilding%20problems%20starts%20with%20the%20workers%2C%20agency%20analysts%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222